sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / DSP API
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant WFC as workflow-controller<br/>Informer Watch
    participant Pod as Workflow Pod
    participant Init as argoexec (init)<br/>Load Artifacts
    participant Main as Main Container<br/>(User Code)
    participant Wait as argoexec (wait)<br/>Save Artifacts
    participant S3 as S3 / MinIO<br/>9000/TCP HTTPS
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP

    Note over User,DB: Flow 1: Workflow Execution

    User->>K8s: POST Workflow CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
    K8s-->>WFC: Watch event (Workflow created)<br/>TLS 1.2+ / ServiceAccount
    WFC->>K8s: Create Pod spec<br/>TLS 1.2+ / ServiceAccount

    Note over Pod,Wait: Pod starts with init + wait containers

    Init->>S3: Download input artifacts<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Access Key/Secret
    S3-->>Init: Artifact data
    Init-->>Main: Artifacts available on volume

    Main->>Main: Execute user workload

    Wait->>Wait: Detect main container completion
    Wait->>S3: Upload output artifacts<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Access Key/Secret
    S3-->>Wait: Upload confirmed
    Wait->>K8s: Create WorkflowTaskResult CR<br/>TLS 1.2+ / ServiceAccount

    K8s-->>WFC: Watch event (TaskResult)<br/>TLS 1.2+ / ServiceAccount
    WFC->>K8s: Update Workflow status<br/>TLS 1.2+ / ServiceAccount
    WFC->>DB: Archive workflow<br/>SSL optional<br/>Auth: Username/Password

    Note over User,DB: Flow 2: Argo Server API Request

    participant Client as Client / Dashboard
    participant Argo as argo-server<br/>2746/TCP HTTPS

    Client->>Argo: GET/POST /api/*<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / SSO
    Argo->>K8s: Kubernetes API call<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Delegated Bearer Token
    K8s-->>Argo: API response
    Argo->>DB: Query archived workflows<br/>SSL optional<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    DB-->>Argo: Workflow data
    Argo->>S3: Fetch artifact for download<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Access Key/Secret
    S3-->>Argo: Artifact data
    Argo-->>Client: JSON/gRPC Response

    Note over User,DB: Flow 3: CronWorkflow Scheduling

    Note right of WFC: Cron controller (internal)<br/>syncs every 10s

    WFC->>K8s: Create Workflow from CronWorkflow<br/>TLS 1.2+ / ServiceAccount
    WFC->>K8s: Update CronWorkflow status<br/>TLS 1.2+ / ServiceAccount
    WFC->>K8s: Delete old Workflows (history limit)<br/>TLS 1.2+ / ServiceAccount
